# Email Template System

Portal uses React Email for creating beautiful, responsive email templates with comprehensive sending capabilities.

## Architecture

### Core Components
- `emails/`: React Email template components
- `emails/components/layout.tsx`: Shared email layout wrapper
- `lib/mail.ts`: Email service configuration (Resend, SMTP, etc.)
- `utils/email.ts`: Email sending utilities and helpers

### Template Structure
- `emails/welcome.tsx`: User welcome email
- `emails/magic-link.tsx`: Magic link authentication email  
- `emails/password-reset.tsx`: Password reset email
- Future templates: Invitation, notification, marketing emails

## Email Templates

### Base Layout Component
```tsx
// emails/components/layout.tsx
import {
  Body,
  Container,
  Head,
  Html,
  Preview,
  Tailwind,
} from '@react-email/components';

interface EmailLayoutProps {
  children: React.ReactNode;
  preview: string;
}

export function EmailLayout({ children, preview }: EmailLayoutProps) {
  return (
    <Html>
      <Head />
      <Preview>{preview}</Preview>
      <Tailwind>
        <Body className="bg-gray-50 font-sans">
          <Container className="mx-auto py-10 px-5">
            <div className="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border p-8">
              {children}
            </div>
          </Container>
        </Body>
      </Tailwind>
    </Html>
  );
}
```

